    "description_long": "This is a single grave monument constructed primarily from polished dark granite and brown stone. The structure features a rectangular base with a raised platform and a prominent upright headstone at one end. The headstone is inscribed with gold lettering, including names, dates, and a short epitaph, and is accompanied by a metallic Latin cross with a figure of Christ. A small vase for flowers is positioned on the right side of the headstone. The monument's surfaces are smooth and glossy, reflecting light, and the overall design is solemn and dignified, typical of modern European cemeteries. The grave marker is solid and heavy, intended to remain fixed in place.",
